juce provides the following CMake targets with permisive license:

    find_package(JUCE CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE
        juce::juce_audio_basics
        juce::juce_core
        juce::juce_events
        juce::juce_audio_devices)

Other targets are also available, see juce's CMakeLists.txt and License for details.
